## Part 1

```elixir
mmin = Enum.min(input_test)
mmax = Enum.max(input_test)

v = for i <- mmin..mmax, do: i

v
|> Enum.map(fn p -> Enum.reduce(input_test, 0, fn i, acc -> abs(i - p) + acc end) end)
|> Enum.min()
```

```output
37
```

